┌─ IDENTITY ──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Binary:    tylluan-nexus (single binary)                     │
│ Port:      :3030 (nativo) │ :3033 (Docker)                  │
│            Docker: :3033 externo → :3030 interno            │
│ Config:    tylluan.toml (gitignored) │ tylluan.example.toml │
│            tylluan.docker.toml (Docker, dev_mode=false)     │
│ Auth:      .tylluan-token (bearer, gitignored)              │
│            Docker: TYLLUAN_TOKEN desde .env (gitignored)    │
│ Data:      data/*.db (sqlite) — gitignored, created on boot │
│ License:   MIT (Forja usa AGPL — nunca mezclar)             │
│ Language:  Rust kernel + Python guilds + React dashboard     │
│ Tests:     431 tests (250 kernel lib + 13 link lib + 168 integration) │ cargo test  │
│ Build:     cargo build -p tylluan-kernel                    │
│ Start:     .\tylluan-mcp.bat (nativo)                       │
│            docker compose up kernel -d (Docker)             │
│ Health:    curl http://127.0.0.1:3030/health (nativo)       │
│            curl http://127.0.0.1:3033/health (Docker)       │
│ Dashboard: npm run dev → http://localhost:5174 (⚠️ NO 5173) │
│            Docker: http://127.0.0.1:3033/                   │
│ MCP:       SSE at /sse │ HTTP Streamable at /messages        │
│                                                              │
│ ⚠️  CRÍTICO: vector_dimensions = 1024 SIEMPRE. NUNCA 768.  │
│    BGE-M3 bug heredado de Forja — Tylluan empieza limpio.   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

