┌─ GUILD SYSTEM (guilds/) ────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                              │
│  Each guild = standalone Python subprocess using fastmcp.    │
│  Kernel spawns them, routes intents, collects results.       │
│                                                              │
│  builders/plugins/    DO things                              │
│    bash.py            shell commands (⚠️ unsandboxed)        │
│    filesystem.py      file read/write/list                   │
│    git.py             version control ops                    │
│    code.py            code execution (⚠️ unsandboxed)        │
│    docker.py          container management                   │
│    database.py        SQL operations                         │
│    formatter.py       code formatting                        │
│                                                              │
│  scholars/plugins/    ANALYZE things                         │
│    knowledge.py       knowledge graph queries                │
│    deep_analysis.py   long-running analysis                  │
│    ingest.py          document ingestion to memory           │
│    pdf.py             PDF text extraction                    │
│    code_analysis.py   AST and code structure                 │
│                                                              │
│  core/                SYSTEM services                        │
│    coloquio.py        agent communication channels           │
│    vision.py          SmolVLM2 image analysis (ONNX, CPU)   │
│    websearch.py       web search                             │
│    deep_web_research.py  DuckDuckGo multi-page research     │
│    mcp_bridge.py      proxy to external MCP servers          │
│                                                              │
│  wardens/plugins/     GUARD quality                          │
│    audit.py           operation logging                      │
│    biome_warden.py    code quality enforcement               │
│                                                              │
│  watchers/plugins/    MONITOR health                         │
│    monitor.py         guild health checks                    │
│    system_metrics.py  CPU/RAM/disk monitoring                │
│                                                              │
│  Routing:  router/catalog.rs has trigger_phrases per guild   │
│  Adding:   1) create .py in guilds/ 2) add to catalog.rs    │
│  Config:   tylluan.toml [guilds.core] always_on list         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

